Cara Menginstall Package Dan Menggunakannya

=============================================

1. ketik "npm init" terus next next
2. kita mau coba gabungkan 3 npm packages yaitu : chalk-rainbow, give-me-a-joke dan cowsay

3. Jangan lupa install paket npm : 
	- npm i chalk-rainbow
	- npm i give-me-a-joke
	- npm i cowsay

4. code Buat index.js :

	const giveMeAJoke = require('give-me-a-joke');
	const chalkRainbow = require('chalk-rainbow');
	const cowsay = require('cowsay');

	// Mendapatkan lelucon dad acak
	giveMeAJoke.getRandomDadJoke(function(joke) {

	  // Mengubah lelucon menjadi suara sapi menggunakan cowsay
  	const cowsayText = cowsay.say({
    	text: chalkRainbow(joke),
    	e: "oO",
    	T: "U"
  	});
  	console.log(cowsayText);
	});

==============================
